maze runner : the death cure ( also known simply as the death cure ) is an upcoming american dystopian science-fiction action thriller film directed by wes ball , based on the death cure , the final book in the maze runner trilogy , written by james dashner , with a screenplay by t.s. nowlin .   it is the sequel to the 2015 film maze runner : the scorch trials and the third and final installment in the maze runner film series .   maze runner : the death cure was originally set to be released on february 17 , 2017 , in the united states by 20th century fox , but the studio rescheduled the film for february 9 , 2018 in 3d , 2d and imax 3d , allowing time for dylan o'brien to fully recover from his injuries sustained on-set .